{"id": 569, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的旧手机都是如何处理的？", "description": "什么？听说要被换了，它选择了自杀。", "record_count": 6588, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183502z608XVkMQO3DNdxI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-13T13:59:47Z", "options": [{"id": 17920, "content": "听歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130933}, {"id": 16897, "content": "丢掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246260}, {"id": 19202, "content": "放回包装盒收起来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263377}, {"id": 16643, "content": "东西都拷进新手机，旧手机卖二手贴补家用^_^", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248223}, {"id": 16900, "content": "什么？我到现在还没换过手机，哪来的旧手机！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250287}, {"id": 17924, "content": "表示习惯几个一起用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255538}, {"id": 17157, "content": "旧手机就是坏了才买新的 当然丢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250080}, {"id": 16646, "content": "一般手机坏了 或者需要过度的时候会起到关键作用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239113}, {"id": 16647, "content": "自从用了苹果，我全家都用苹果了", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197716}, {"id": 44039, "content": "碎尸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440413}, {"id": 16649, "content": "留着收藏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117509}, {"id": 16650, "content": "一直想拆 但是并没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232869}, {"id": 16651, "content": "静静地躺在抽屉里，七年后终于无法充电开机了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 16652, "content": "像个旧玩具一样，有点心疼但是不愿去动", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248302}, {"id": 16653, "content": "我都是坏了才换。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248311}, {"id": 16654, "content": "垫桌脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248329}, {"id": 16655, "content": "放起来，也许有天会用上，也许迟早扔了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248330}, {"id": 16656, "content": "老妈肾6 妹妹肾5 我用4s 老爹用4……这可都是代代相传下来的啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170559}, {"id": 16657, "content": "我觉得还是做备用机用比较好，如果实在太多就选择手机回收♻️速得回收掉就好了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 247773}, {"id": 17426, "content": "旧手机都是因为坏了不能用了……但是老爹总会想出办法修好自己用，再给我买新的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253380}, {"id": 16659, "content": "把内容删完给丈母娘用！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248349}, {"id": 18453, "content": "旧的卖点加钱买新的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259231}, {"id": 19223, "content": "对于一部充满了记忆和回忆的老手机，我会选择收藏它一辈子，或许永远不会再打开，或许也无法再打开，但是看到它就会唤起自己心里难以忘记的回忆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263459}, {"id": 19479, "content": "包装好珍藏起来。现在见到十年前的诺基亚和摩托罗拉，你们什么心情？以后还会有的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265001}, {"id": 19480, "content": "老婆买了64G的5S，我获得9成新的5…老婆买了128的白6P，我获得9成新5S…老婆买了128的玫瑰金，我获得9成新的6P，基本就是这样( ¯ᒡ̱¯ )و", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265030}, {"id": 17945, "content": "想卖掉，但又舍不得", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256353}, {"id": 16666, "content": "闲置", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164080}, {"id": 16668, "content": "旧手机自己藏起来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181688}, {"id": 16669, "content": "不断给爸妈更新换代，然后最古老的手机就躺在我家抽屉里，试问貌似清除数据卖掉、好像也有办法还原数据？不知是否安全？?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248413}, {"id": 16670, "content": "一年换了七部手机，要是知道好方法我也不会那样造了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244389}, {"id": 16926, "content": "放在家当纪念品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232053}, {"id": 18462, "content": "躺在那里睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259241}, {"id": 16673, "content": "可以自己备用，或者给孩子当玩具，或者给老人使用，或者送人，或者收藏，反正用处挺多！就看你怎么用？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248442}, {"id": 16675, "content": "还能用。换着用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248475}, {"id": 16676, "content": "收藏", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245538}, {"id": 16677, "content": "火化了。", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211322o0AVWOUdsD8BZp4r.jpg", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248512}, {"id": 16678, "content": "我妈用完了给我爸，我爸用完了我用，这就是等级压制????", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 243005}, {"id": 20518, "content": "留着看视频用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266337}, {"id": 17449, "content": "我淘汰的给我爸 我把淘汰的给我姥姥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253535}, {"id": 21037, "content": "用到不能再用 再换电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274848}, {"id": 18734, "content": "从来没有旧手机，新手机的到来都是因为旧手机丢得猝不及防", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260649}, {"id": 16687, "content": "留着留着留着……就坏了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248583}, {"id": 16688, "content": "收藏着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170610}, {"id": 16689, "content": "留着打游戏啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235166}, {"id": 17969, "content": "等以后科技发达了，把它修好，把以前的短信找出来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254829}, {"id": 16690, "content": "拿来高三用咯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232954}, {"id": 16946, "content": "给老爸了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225869}, {"id": 17202, "content": "真的不想仍，也不想卖，就是留着，想起来了充充电，看看开机画面，然后再关机放抽屉里╮(╯_╰)╭我是个怀旧的人啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169698}, {"id": 17459, "content": "留着，做纪念也好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228570}, {"id": 16692, "content": "没用", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211145gcNDrV7Imn5JAizG.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248649}]}